Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    The Board class is the abstract superclass for the concrete classes StaticBoard and DynamicBoard.
    DynamicBoard
    DynamicBoard is a concrete implementation of the abstract Board class.
    FileHandler
    The FileHandler class handles the reading and writing of RLE-files from and to disk.
    GameOfLife
    The GameOfLife class represents the logic behind this implementation of Conway's Game of Life.
    GifConstructor
    The GifConstructor class interacts with lieng.GIFWriter and sends all necessary information in order to create a gif of the current pattern or board.
    Main
    This is the driver class for this implementation of Game of Life.
    StaticBoard Deprecated
    replaced by DynamicBoard
    Statistics
    Statistics is a implementation of the statistics in the game.
    ThreadWorker
    The ThreadWorker class keeps track of a FixedThreadPool and is responsible for thread management while GameOfLife is running concurrently.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PatternFormatException
    PatternFormatException is an exception thrown when reading a file whose RLE-pattern is formatted wrong.
    RulesFormatException
    RulesFormatException is an exception thrown when trying to load a rule set that is formatted wrong or is invalid.
